        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 10. Aulodrilus dentosus sp. nov. from Lake Kitaura, Japan. A, parasagittal section of anterior part of body; B, parasagittal section of genital segments; C, cross section at the level of spermathecal pores in VI; D, the same at the level of male pores in VII; E, longitudinal section of atrium and penis; F, cross section of atrium at the junction with prostate gland." ;
